<h2 class="titleplus1">
	<a href="/en/2020/covid-19-5124627">
    	<span class="strapline">Sport in times of Covid-19: </span>
    	Will football go bust?	</a></h2>
<div class="chapeau"> 
    <a href="/en/2020/covid-19-5124627">
